bajingan seperti dia.

00:04:26.198 --> 00:04:28.782
Semua berkat rahmat Tuhan.
- Ya..

00:04:29.906 --> 00:04:30.989
Tunggu apa lagi?

00:04:31.323 --> 00:04:32.698
Meninggalkan!  - Meninggalkan!

00:04:33.156 --> 00:04:34.905
Yuvraj, pergilah, kataku!

